{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"story_firwhl_set_1_story_1","storyGroup":"story_firwhl_set_1","storySort":0,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":null,"storyName":"独行之人","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"","storyCanEnter":0,"storyTxt":"obt/memory/story_firwhl_1_1","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":0,"requiredStages":null,"characters":["浮夸的学生","文静的学生","阿格妮","学生们","村长","活泼的孩子","阿格妮的父亲"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_bg_27_g26_dusk_wild.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/a001/m_dia_path_loop.mp3","volume":"0.8","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":8},{"type":"charslot","id":9},{"type":"dialogue","name":"浮夸的学生","text":"终于，我们终于等到了封顶的这一天！","id":10},{"type":"charslot","id":11},{"type":"dialogue","name":"浮夸的学生","text":"我们第一次走出大学，走出移动城市，花了整整两个星期，用自己的双手，一砖一瓦地劳动......","id":12},{"type":"charslot","id":13},{"type":"dialogue","name":"浮夸的学生","text":"为这座在贫穷与困苦中挣扎的村庄建起了一所学校！","id":14},{"type":"charslot","id":15},{"type":"dialogue","name":"浮夸的学生","text":"哦，我耳边已经响起了孩子们的读书声......","id":16},{"type":"text","text":"村庄边缘的空地上，十几个大学生模样的人正围坐在一起，兴奋地叽叽喳喳。","id":17},{"type":"text","text":"他们身边，一座刚刚建成的二层建筑歪歪扭扭地立着。","id":18},{"type":"charslot","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"文静的学生","text":"得了吧你，诗不是诗，散文不是散文，我听得都要反酸水了。","id":20},{"type":"charslot","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"文静的学生","text":"说实话，阿格妮，能给村子建起这所学校，你才是最重要的因素。","id":22},{"type":"dialog","id":23},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#10$1","duration":"1.5","id":24},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"哈哈，哪有。","id":26,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"文静的学生","text":"我是说真的。","id":28},{"type":"charslot","id":29},{"type":"dialogue","name":"文静的学生","text":"我们这帮高谈阔论的大学生，整天说要帮助雷姆必拓的穷人，却连移动城市之外的人怎么生活都没见过。","id":30},{"type":"charslot","id":31},{"type":"dialogue","name":"文静的学生","text":"要不是你提醒我们要脚踏实地，我们绝对不可能亲眼目睹这座村庄的贫穷——","id":32},{"type":"charslot","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"浮夸的学生","text":"诸位，让我们花点时间，祝福这座饱含我们心意的建筑！","id":34},{"type":"charslot","id":35},{"type":"dialogue","name":"文静的学生","text":"呃，他又要搞什么......","id":36},{"type":"text","text":"浮夸的学生从怀里掏出一瓶香槟，握在手中使劲摇晃。","id":37},{"type":"text","text":"伴着四处泼溅的香槟酒，瓶塞喷射而出，好巧不巧，正好嵌在学校歪斜的大门和门框中间。","id":38},{"type":"charslot","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"学生们","text":"哈哈哈哈哈哈......","id":40},{"type":"charslot","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"文静的学生","text":"哈哈哈......阿格妮，这家伙简直......太离谱了......","id":42},{"type":"charslot","id":43},{"type":"dialogue","name":"文静的学生","text":"阿格妮，怎么了？你看起来一点都不高兴。","id":44},{"type":"text","text":"阿格妮指了指远处的村民们。","id":45},{"type":"text","text":"就仿佛刚刚建好的学校和建起学校的大学生们都不存在一样，他们只是埋头劳作，谁的脸上都没有一丝笑意。","id":46},{"type":"dialog","id":47},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":48},{"type":"charslot","id":49},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e6/Avg_bg_bg_snowconutryinside.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":50},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":51},{"type":"dialog","id":52},{"type":"playsound","key":"$doorknockquite","id":53},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":54},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"谁啊？","id":56,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":57},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"村长先生，您好，我是阿格妮，来建学校的大学生。","id":58},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"太晚了，有什么事明天说吧。","id":60,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"明天我们就走了，我来道个别。","id":62},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"不用道别，你们乐意什么时候走都行。","id":64,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"不，不光是道别，还有别的事......","id":66},{"type":"dialog","id":67},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","volume":"1","id":68},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":69},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":70},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":71},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":72},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"其实是今天我们疯过头了，忘了把这个给你们。","id":73,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#11$1","id":74},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"给，庆祝学校落成的酒。","id":75,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/15/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":76},{"type":"charslot","id":77},{"type":"text","text":"见村长没有接的意思，阿格妮只能自己把酒瓶放在木桌上。","id":78},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"乡下人喝不惯，你拿回去吧。","id":80,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#11$1","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"这酒很好入口，不信您可以试试。","id":82,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/15/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":83},{"type":"charslot","id":84},{"type":"text","text":"村长摇了摇头，拿起桌上的酒瓶，试图找到一些自己能理解的图画。","id":85},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":86},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"这画的什么？葡萄园？葡萄园和“香槟”有什么关系？","id":87,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#10$1","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"反正是酒商瞎画的图，瞎起的名字，您就把它当成一般的起泡酒就行。","id":89,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":90},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"哼，我们自己酿的酒，也不比什么香槟差。","id":91,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#10$1","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"那——明天出发前，我们要不要来个交换品酒？我们也尝一尝村子的自酿酒——","id":93,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"早没了。","id":95,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"自从周围发现铁矿，别说种啤酒花了，连源石虫都不愿意在这儿筑巢。","id":97,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#4$1","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"怎么会呢。","id":99,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"“怎么会”？","id":101,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"你们来这儿这么多天，就没听见过采矿平台发出的声音？时不时震上一下，偶尔地动山摇，源石虫能不躲着走吗？","id":103,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#8$1","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"前几天好像是有采矿平台的动静，可我们都没注意到......","id":105,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":106},{"type":"charslot","id":107},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":108},{"type":"playsound","key":"$smallearthquake","volume":"0.1","id":109},{"type":"text","text":"仿佛要给村民的话作注脚似的，远处真的传来隆隆的轰鸣声。","id":110},{"type":"dialog","id":111},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":112},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"这下注意到了？","id":114,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":115,"musicid":1},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":116},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"小姑娘，带着你的酒回去吧。","id":117,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#5$1","id":118},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"可是......","id":119,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":120},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"你还有什么事？","id":121,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#6$1","id":122},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"我其实就是想问问，为什么一开始大家都很欢迎我们，可现在学校建成了，大家反而显得冷淡了？是我们有哪里做得不好吗？","id":123,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9b/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#6$1","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"如果是因为学校的建筑质量不行，我得负起责任，找个更靠谱的施工队来——","id":125,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9b/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":126},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"反正你们也要走了，我直说吧。","id":127,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":128},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"村里根本不需要什么学校。","id":129,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#4$1","id":130},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"什么？","id":131,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":132},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"我们不过是想，你们一来，村子就能多点收入。吃饭、住宿，万一再捐点什么东西......这不都是钱吗？","id":133,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":134},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"可你们倒好，村里的饭不吃，村里的房不住，居然在空地上搭帐篷......","id":135,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"这几天，除了帮你们砍树烧砖，村里唯一做成的生意就是烤兽肉，这点钱够干什么？谁能高兴得起来？","id":137,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#8$1","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"可只要把眼光放长远，学校建成了，村里的孩子就能受到教育，改变现在的生活——","id":139,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":140},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"改变现在的生活？我们为什么要改变自己的生活？","id":141,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":142},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"算了，我不跟你提那些虚的，我现在就问你一个问题。","id":143,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":144},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"谁来上课？哪个老师愿意来这种没前途的地方教学生？他自己去移动城市不好吗？去给你们这些有钱人家的孩子当家教不好吗？","id":145,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":146},{"type":"charslot","id":147},{"type":"text","text":"“当”的一声，村长把酒瓶杵回桌上。","id":148},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#6$1","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"是我们......是我想得太浅了。","id":150,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9b/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#6$1","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"我以为只要建起学校，再加上合理的薪资，就一定会有人来应聘......","id":152,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9b/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"我们这儿既没有矿，也没和矿业公司签什么合同，他们的商路都绕开这里。就算多出点钱，谁愿意每天穿过荒地来给人上课？","id":154,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"咱们本来就不是一路人，别白费工夫了。回去吧。","id":156,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"酒你也拿回去。","id":158,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#7$1","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"不，至少......","id":160,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#7$1","id":161},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"您稍等一会儿！","id":162,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":163},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":164},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1","id":165},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":166},{"type":"dialog","id":167},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":168},{"type":"charslot","id":169},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_bg_27_g26_dusk_wild.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":170},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":171},{"type":"charslot","id":172},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"浮夸的学生","text":"留下来当老师？","id":174},{"type":"charslot","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"浮夸的学生","text":"这个我真帮不上忙，抱歉，阿格妮。","id":176},{"type":"charslot","id":177},{"type":"dialogue","name":"文静的学生","text":"我们拿钱给他们雇老师好不好？","id":178},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#8$1","id":179},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"我也想过，可这里交通不便，没人愿意来，只有我们......","id":180,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":181},{"type":"dialogue","name":"文静的学生","text":"阿格妮，你忘了？再有五天就开学了。","id":182},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#8$1","id":183},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"......开学？","id":184,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"文静的学生","text":"我还得抓紧时间多修几个学分，否则就延毕了。","id":186},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#4$1","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"开学？学分？延毕？！","id":188,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"文静的学生","text":"阿......阿格妮？","id":190},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#2$1","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"（深呼吸）","id":192,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/18/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#1$1","id":193},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"我不是怪你们，但这里的孩子根本没学上，我们却要因为开学而走人，你们难道不觉得......讽刺吗？","id":194,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"文静的学生","text":"可我们首先是大学生，学生就应该按时到校，这不是天经地义吗？","id":196},{"type":"text","text":"阿格妮站在原地，好像有很多话想说，又什么都说不出来。","id":197},{"type":"text","text":"其余的学生安慰了阿格妮几句，见她没有反应，只能各自散去。","id":198},{"type":"text","text":"他们还有行李要收拾，还有学分要修，还有文凭要拿，没时间在这里陪阿格妮一起站着。","id":199},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":200},{"type":"dialog","id":201},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":202},{"type":"charslot","id":203},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":204},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_bg_27_g26_dusk_wild.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":205},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":206},{"type":"charslot","id":207},{"type":"playsound","key":"$sportscarstart","volume":"0.8","id":208},{"type":"delay","time":"4","id":209},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"现在喊一嗓子追上去，你还能坐上车。","id":211,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#7$1","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"我既然决定要留下来，就不会改主意。","id":213,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":214},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"要我说，你留下来当老师也没用。","id":215,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#7$1","id":216},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"至少现在，我自己觉得有用。","id":217,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"那你可够倔的。","id":219,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#7$1","id":220},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"我从小就倔得要死，认准一件事就不松口，我爸妈都头疼死了。","id":221,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":222},{"type":"charslot","id":223},{"type":"text","text":"两人转过身，慢慢往村子的方向走去。","id":224},{"type":"dialog","id":225},{"type":"dialog","id":226},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":227},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":228},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$newhope01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta3_181101/m_dia_newhope01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.8","id":229,"musicid":2},{"type":"text","text":"村民们对学校、老师一类的名词并不热心，但大人们忙着维持生计，白天没人看孩子也是事实。","id":230},{"type":"text","text":"于是，回到村庄的阿格妮如愿以偿地获得了村民们的许可，还像模像样地排了课表，做了教案。","id":231},{"type":"text","text":"可刚开始上课，阿格妮就发现，她以为自己要教的是加减乘除，可孩子们连最基础的读和写都还没掌握。","id":232},{"type":"text","text":"几天的教学下来，她和孩子们都累得要命。","id":233},{"type":"dialog","id":234},{"type":"charslot","id":235},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e6/Avg_bg_bg_snowconutryinside.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":236},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":237},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":238},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"大家都看出来了，你是认真想教孩子们学点东西。你比你那帮同学强太多了，阿格妮。","id":239,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":240},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"但是，我劝你对自己好一点，带孩子们玩玩闹闹去吧。别把自己搞得太累了。","id":241,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#2$1","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"如果我偏不呢？","id":243,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/18/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"那你又能做到什么？","id":245,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"你最多教孩子们认几个字，算几个数，可这又能有多大用？","id":247,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#1$1","id":248},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"怎么会没用呢？","id":249,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#10$1","id":250},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"这些都是最基础的知识，只有掌握了这些，才有可能开始更高层次的学习，进而改变生活......","id":251,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":252},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"又来了，改变生活。","id":253,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"阿格妮，村里人喜欢你，是因为你热心、善良、不图回报，不是因为你想改变大家的生活。","id":255,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":256},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"你知道这么多年来，是谁害得我们的生活改来改去，连啤酒都改没了的吗？是矿业公司。","id":257,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#8$1","id":258},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"但是，假如孩子们能掌握更多的知识，拥有更开阔的眼界，他们一定能过得更好。","id":259,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"怎么过得更好？进大学？","id":261,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#1$1","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"对，这也是“更好”的一部分。","id":263,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":264},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"那你准备花多长时间教出一个和你一样的大学生？","id":265,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#1$1","id":266},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"......我知道我自己现在像个傻瓜，但对我来说，半途而废比完全不做更难受。","id":267,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"你确实够倔。我要是你爸妈，我也会头疼死的。","id":269,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":270},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"随你的便吧。","id":271,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":272},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#8$1","id":273},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":274},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"我记得那瓶香槟还在这放着，没错吧？","id":275,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":276},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"你要喝？","id":277,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#10$1","id":278},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"哈哈，那是留着做庆功酒的，现在喝算什么，借酒浇愁吗？","id":279,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#8$1","id":280},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"其实......今天正好是大学开学的日子。","id":281,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#8$1","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"从今天算起，要是我能给孩子们上一个学期的课......","id":283,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#10$1","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"不管孩子们学得怎么样，等到学期结束那天，我们就和村里人一起把这瓶酒开了，你看怎么样？","id":285,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":286},{"type":"charslot","id":287},{"type":"text","text":"村长看了看阿格妮，又看了看放在破橱柜最深处，华丽得与周遭格格不入的香槟酒。","id":288},{"type":"text","text":"伴着远处采矿平台钻探的声音，瓶中的气泡不安分地向上浮去，试图挣脱液面的阻拦。","id":289},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":290},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"你拿来的酒，听你的。","id":291,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":292},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":293},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":294},{"type":"text","text":"在那之后，孩子们学会了写自己的名字，学会了加和减，一部分聪明的孩子已经学到了乘和除。","id":295},{"type":"text","text":"而在教学之余，凭借着从小到大的玩火经验，阿格妮也在村民心中获得了一定的地位——","id":296},{"type":"text","text":"至少，一家人饿着肚子，湿柴却不起火只冒烟的时候，所有人的第一反应都成了“快去找阿格妮”。","id":297},{"type":"text","text":"一个月时间很快过去。","id":298},{"type":"dialog","id":299},{"type":"charslot","id":300},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e6/Avg_bg_bg_snowconutryinside.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":301},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":302},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#11$1","id":303},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"（伸懒腰）","id":304,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/15/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#11$1","id":305},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"今天的课终于上完了......","id":306,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/15/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":307},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"累了？","id":308,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#10$1","id":309},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"我还挺得住。","id":310,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#10$1","id":311},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"你想，我们用一个月完成了正常学校一个半月的教学任务。要是往短了算，一学期的课业进度已经过半了！","id":312,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#9$1","id":313},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"也就是说，只要再过一个月，就是开香槟的日子——","id":314,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":315},{"type":"dialogue","name":"活泼的孩子","text":"阿格妮老师，阿格妮老师！","id":316},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#4$1","id":317},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"怎么了？","id":318,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":319},{"type":"dialogue","name":"活泼的孩子","text":"阿格妮老师，村口来了一队汽车，里面有一位穿得很整齐的老伯，他指名要找你！","id":320},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#8$1","id":321},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"......","id":322,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"活泼的孩子","text":"老师，你怎么了？","id":324},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#11$1","id":325},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"......没事。","id":326,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/15/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":327},{"type":"dialogue","name":"活泼的孩子","text":"那我去玩了！","id":328},{"type":"dialog","id":329},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":330},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":331},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":332},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"你父亲？","id":333,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#5$1","id":334},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"......多半是他。","id":335,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#5$1","id":336},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"看来这瓶酒，我是喝不到了。","id":337,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":338},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"（拍拍阿格妮的肩膀）","id":339,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":340},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"会替你留着的。你还是先去见你父亲吧。","id":341,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":342},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":343},{"type":"charslot","id":344},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_bg_27_g26_dusk_wild.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":345},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":346},{"type":"charslot","id":347},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$mist_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_mist_loop.mp3","volume":"0.8","id":348,"musicid":3},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#1$1","id":349},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"爸。","id":350,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":351},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮的父亲","text":"让我看看......还好，还好，没受什么伤，就是瘦了点。","id":352},{"type":"charslot","id":353},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮的父亲","text":"你疯也疯够了，该回去收收心了。","id":354},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#1$1","id":355},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"我不回去。我和村里人约好教他们的孩子一个学期的课，现在课才上了一半。","id":356,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":357},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮的父亲","text":"（叹气）","id":358},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#1$1","id":359},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"我们用一个月上了半个学期的课，孩子们已经学会了写自己的名字，学会了加减法！只要再有一个月就能结课了！","id":360,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":361},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮的父亲","text":"阿格妮，你明知道这没意义。","id":362},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#3$1","id":363},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"没意义？！","id":364,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6b/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":365},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮的父亲","text":"就凭会写自己的名字，会算加减法，那些孩子就能成为和他们的父母不一样的人吗？","id":366},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#7$1","id":367},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"......","id":368,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":369},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮的父亲","text":"回学校吧。","id":370},{"type":"charslot","id":371},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮的父亲","text":"时间不等人。你晚一年毕业，我就得晚一年把矿上的担子交到你手里——","id":372},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#3$1","id":373},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"我说过多少次了，我不想继承你的矿！","id":374,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6b/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":375},{"type":"charslot","id":376},{"type":"text","text":"车队的其他人全都默不作声。","id":377},{"type":"text","text":"这样父女吵架的场景，他们也不知见过多少次了。","id":378},{"type":"charslot","id":379},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮的父亲","text":"阿格妮，我也说过很多次，我很庆幸自己有一个善良的女儿，知道为其他人着想，知道自己能生在一个富裕的家庭里有多幸运。","id":380},{"type":"charslot","id":381},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮的父亲","text":"但她不愿意想，要让其他人过上更好的日子，她必须站在更高的位置上，从统筹全局的角度为别人谋福利。","id":382},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#3$1","id":383},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"别聊这个了好不好，聊不出结果的！","id":384,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6b/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":385},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮的父亲","text":"......你甚至不愿意听我把话说完。","id":386},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#7$1","id":387},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"......","id":388,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":389},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮的父亲","text":"这样吧，阿格妮，我们做个约定。","id":390},{"type":"charslot","id":391},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮的父亲","text":"你不是担心孩子们的课没人上吗？我可以帮你为村子雇一位老师。只要薪酬够高，会有人愿意来的。","id":392},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#7$1","id":393},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"终于开始了？用我关心的人做筹码，让我接受你的条件？","id":394,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":395},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮的父亲","text":"别这样，阿格妮。","id":396},{"type":"charslot","id":397},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮的父亲","text":"我只希望，当我做了这些之后，你可以认真想一想我的话。","id":398},{"type":"charslot","id":399},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮的父亲","text":"想一想，如果你在我的位置上，甚至掌握比我更多的资源的时候，你能为这座村庄......能为更多座这样的村庄做什么。","id":400},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#7$1","id":401},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"......","id":402,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":403},{"type":"charslot","id":404},{"type":"text","text":"阿格妮低着头，咬紧牙关，不敢看父亲的眼睛。","id":405},{"type":"text","text":"因为她害怕，和父亲对视的那一刻，自己就会点头。","id":406},{"type":"text","text":"她为这样的自己感到恶心。","id":407},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#7$1","id":408},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"（咬牙）","id":409,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#7$1","id":410},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"我去村子里......说这件事。","id":411,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":412},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":413},{"type":"charslot","id":414},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e6/Avg_bg_bg_snowconutryinside.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":415},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":416},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#7$1","id":417},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"我走，他来找老师......就是这样。","id":418,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":419},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"所以你家里......","id":420,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":421},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"果然是开矿的。","id":422,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#7$1","id":423},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"（沉默地点头）","id":424,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":425},{"type":"charslot","id":426},{"type":"text","text":"村长从橱柜深处掏出那瓶香槟酒，塞在阿格妮怀里。","id":427},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":428},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"阿格妮，你走吧。","id":429,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":430},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"我们本来就不需要学校，现在更不需要一所矿老板资助的学校。","id":431,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#5$1","id":432},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"您别这样......","id":433,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":434},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"我不得不这样。","id":435,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":436},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"我跟你说过，自从周围发现铁矿，村子里连源石虫都不筑巢了。那我有没有跟你说过，为什么村子里连啤酒花都不种了？","id":437,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#5$1","id":438},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"没有......","id":439,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":440},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"走，出去转转，我告诉你为什么。","id":441,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":442},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":443},{"type":"charslot","id":444},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_bg_27_g26_dusk_wild.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":445},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":446},{"type":"charslot","id":447},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":448},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"你看这些荒地，以前种满了啤酒花，现在已经完全撂荒了。","id":449,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#5$1","id":450},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"......","id":451,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":452},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"采矿平台刚建起来的时候，我们想的是，矿业公司一来，这里肯定会来很多矿工，会多出很多物资需求......","id":453,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":454},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"正是我们和矿业公司做生意的好机会。","id":455,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":456},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"可他们没来找我们。","id":457,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":458},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"他们自己建立了供应链和贸易点，向所有人开放，里面简直应有尽有，粮食、水果、粗布......对，还有啤酒。","id":459,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":460},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"他们的价格甚至比我们的成本还低！","id":461,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":462},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"很快，别说和矿业公司做生意，就连以前和我们互通有无的那些村庄也不来买东西了，毕竟矿业公司的货既便宜又好用。","id":463,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":464},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"所以我们不种啤酒花了，因为根本没人来买我们的啤酒，连村里人想喝酒时首先想到的也是矿业公司。","id":465,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":466},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"这时矿业公司的人倒来了，告诉我们，只要签订土地转让协定，就能在拿到补偿款的同时被矿业公司雇佣，待遇从优......","id":467,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":468},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"哼，待遇从优！","id":469,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":470},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"我可从别人嘴里听说，所谓的雇佣，就是矿业公司可以随时让你卷铺盖走人，到时候你不光没了收入，连一片能种庄稼的土地都没有了！","id":471,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":472},{"type":"charslot","id":473},{"type":"text","text":"看着眼前激动的村长，阿格妮想起父亲刚刚说的话。","id":474},{"type":"text","text":"“想一想，如果你在我的位置上，甚至掌握比我更多的资源的时候，你能为这座村庄......能为更多座这样的村庄做什么。”","id":475},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":476},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"而你，阿格妮......我愿意相信你，你真的只是怀着善意来教孩子们读写的。","id":477,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":478},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"可现在你告诉我，你要走了，你父亲的矿业公司会资助这所学校......我拿什么相信他，相信他的公司？","id":479,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":480},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"还有——","id":481,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":482},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"我知道这句话可能过头了，但是，阿格妮——","id":483,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":484},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"你不觉得你在和你父亲，和你父亲的竞争对手们做一样的事吗？","id":485,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#4$1","id":486},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"怎么可能？！我怎么会和他们一样？！","id":487,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":488},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"你们都一样，你们想让我们的后代失去他们的土地，去采矿平台，去移动城市，去过朝不保夕的生活。","id":489,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":490},{"type":"charslot","id":491},{"type":"text","text":"阿格妮颤抖着嘴唇，她有一万句话想说，但她一句也说不出。","id":492},{"type":"dialog","id":493},{"type":"playsound","key":"$smallearthquake","volume":"0.6","id":494},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"3","xstrength":"4","ystrength":"4","vibrato":"20","randomness":"30","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":495},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":496},{"type":"text","text":"远处传来轰鸣声。","id":497},{"type":"text","text":"在村子里住了这么长时间，阿格妮已经习惯了这样的轰鸣和震动，但这次比平时剧烈许多。","id":498},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":499},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"他妈的，这次怎么震得这么厉害？！","id":500,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":501},{"type":"charslot","id":502},{"type":"text","text":"在村庄不远处，一座大型采矿平台以极近的距离隆隆驶过村庄，引发的震动就宛如预示着天灾到来的地震。","id":503},{"type":"text","text":"阿格妮一个趔趄，终于理解了为什么连源石虫都不愿在这里筑巢。","id":504},{"type":"text","text":"但她的余光瞥到了别的东西。","id":505},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#4$1","id":506},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"学校！！","id":507,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":508},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"学校？！","id":509,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":510},{"type":"charslot","id":511},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"1.5","block":"false","id":512},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_rockfall","volume":"1","id":513},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":514},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":515},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":516},{"type":"text","text":"大型采矿平台渐渐远去，引发的震动也逐渐平息。","id":517},{"type":"text","text":"而那座出自外行之手，本就摇摇欲坠的二层建筑，已经被震成了一地瓦砾。","id":518},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#4$1","id":519},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"......","id":520,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":521},{"type":"charslot","id":522},{"type":"text","text":"直到震动完全消失，阿格妮才跌坐在地。","id":523},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":524},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"你应该庆幸现在放学了，里面没人。","id":525,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":526},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"......","id":527,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":528},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"回去吧，阿格妮，别替我们操心了。","id":529,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_006","id":530},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村长","text":"你是个好姑娘，但我早说过了，咱们不是一路人。","id":531,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_006.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":532},{"type":"charslot","id":533},{"type":"text","text":"村长扔下阿格妮，往自己家走去。","id":534},{"type":"text","text":"他走了不远的一段路，回头看了看，阿格妮还站在那里。","id":535},{"type":"text","text":"真是个倔姑娘，他想，但这个倔姑娘最后也会和她父亲一样，变成一个没那么讨厌，但更危险的体面人。","id":536},{"type":"text","text":"正当他这么想着，打算回头走路的时候，他看到，阿格妮抓起放在地上的香槟酒。","id":537},{"type":"text","text":"他看到，阿格妮双手攥住香槟瓶，近乎疯狂地摇晃起来，仿佛里面囚禁着的不是气泡，而是谁的灵魂。","id":538},{"type":"text","text":"他看到，为了摇那瓶香槟，阿格妮几乎耗尽了全身力气，摇到连最后一丝力气都耗尽的时候，她把酒瓶高举过头，瓶口直指天空。","id":539},{"type":"text","text":"砰。","id":540},{"type":"text","text":"他听得不很真切。","id":541},{"type":"text","text":"但他分明看到，瓶塞直直朝天飞去，也许在最后不得已落在瓦砾堆里，也许没有。","id":542},{"type":"text","text":"他最后看到的是，阿格妮狠狠把香槟瓶摔到地上，然后大步走开。","id":543},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":544},{"type":"dialog","id":545},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":546},{"type":"charslot","id":547},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_bg_27_g26_dusk_wild.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":548},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":549},{"type":"charslot","id":550},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.8","id":551,"musicid":4},{"type":"charslot","id":552},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮的父亲","text":"阿格妮，已经好几个小时了，你一句话也不说。","id":553},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#8$1","id":554},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"......","id":555,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":556},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮的父亲","text":"这样闹别扭解决不了任何问题。","id":557},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#8$1","id":558},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"......","id":559,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":560},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮的父亲","text":"阿格妮，你得正视现实。矿业越发展，这样的村庄就越没有希望。","id":561},{"type":"charslot","id":562},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮的父亲","text":"可他们只要愿意放弃过去，拥抱那个唾手可得的未来，那么，不管是他们，还是他们的后代，都有机会过上真正富足的生活。","id":563},{"type":"charslot","id":564},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮的父亲","text":"而我，还有未来的你，就是为了让这样的愿景成真而工作的。","id":565},{"type":"charslot","id":566},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮的父亲","text":"只不过你现在还不明白，为了给他们更好的生活，我们要先劝他们从过去的幻梦里走出来。这个过程拖得越短，痛苦就越少。","id":567},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#7$1","id":568},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"（干笑）","id":569,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#7$1","id":570},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"......那我告诉你，爸，这个过程刚刚前进了一大步。","id":571,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#7$1","id":572},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"我们给村子建的那个学校塌了。被经过的采矿平台震塌的。","id":573,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":574},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮的父亲","text":"震塌了？","id":575},{"type":"charslot","id":576},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮的父亲","text":"那时地面震得确实很厉害，我没注意到。我会帮你把学校重新修起来——","id":577},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#7$1","id":578},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"你......难道在担心我们之前的约定还算不算数？","id":579,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":580},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮的父亲","text":"......","id":581},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#7$1","id":582},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"不用担心。","id":583,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#8$1","id":584},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"我确实很认真地想了你说的话，从一上车就在想，一直想到现在。","id":585,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#8$1","id":586},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"我觉得自己还是有很多事没想通——几乎什么都没想通。","id":587,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#7$1","id":588},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"但我至少想通了一件事。","id":589,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":590},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮的父亲","text":"......","id":591},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#1$1","id":592},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"说真心话，你是个好雇主，好公民，你是个......好父亲。","id":593,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#1$1","id":594},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"但雷姆必拓永远不缺体面的好人。","id":595,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#8$1","id":596},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"爸，我怕，我真的怕体面人当得太久，我会看不见身边发生的事情，比如......一座学校的倒塌。","id":597,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#1$1","id":598},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"所以我不会继承你的产业......","id":599,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_493_firwhl_1#1$1","id":600},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿格妮","text":"......爸爸。","id":601,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_avg_493_firwhl_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":602},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":603},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":604},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":605},{"type":"character","id":606},{"type":"image","id":607}],"characters":["浮夸的学生","文静的学生","阿格妮","学生们","村长","活泼的孩子","阿格妮的父亲"]}